Project description

TF.Text is a TensorFlow library of text related ops, modules, and subgraphs. Thelibrary can perform the preprocessing regularly required by text-based models,and includes other features useful for sequence modeling not provided by coreTensorFlow.

See the README on GitHub for further documentation.http://github.com/tensorflow/text
